{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-input"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Input</h3>
        <p>Receiving data is a key interaction point for users of websites. NDS has several types of input components to help get information from users.</p>

        <h4>Checkbox</h4>
        <p>Checkboxes are used when multiple options of a set can be selected simultaneously. See the Checkbox Input Group (molecule - input-group-checkbox) to create a group of checkboxes.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-checkbox/demo/input-checkbox.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Radio Button</h4>
        <p>Radio buttons are used when only one option of a set can be selected at a time. See the Radio Input Group (molecule: input-group-radio) to create a group of radio buttons.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-radio/demo/input-radio.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Text Input</h4>
        <p>Text fields have a variety of uses, from gathering usernames and passwords to filling out contact information. To create a complete text field, see the Text Input Group (molecule - input-group-text).</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-text/demo/input-text.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Text Input with Icon</h4>
        <p>This component is a variation on the Text Input component and includes the ability to add a Font Awesome icon in the field.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-text/demo/input-text-icon.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Select (Dropdown)</h4>
        <p>Single choice select fields can be used in place of radio buttons.</p>
        <p>NDS uses the <a href="https://select2.org/">Select2 JS</a> library to enhance the functionality and usability of select (dropdown) fields. The nds-select="true" attribute must be present on the select HTML element for a select field to use the Select2 functionality.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-select/demo/input-select.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Multiselect (Dropdown)</h4>
        <p>Multiple choice select fields can be used in the place of checkboxes.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-select/demo/input-multiselect.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Datepicker</h4>
        <p>NDS uses <a href="https://bootstrap-datepicker.readthedocs.io/en/latest/">Bootstrap Datepicker</a> to make the experience of selecting a date in a form easier. The nds-date-picker="true" attribute must be present on the input HTML element for datepicker to be initialized.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/input/input-date-picker/demo/input-date-picker.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>
{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-layouts"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Layouts</h3>
        <h4>Site Layout</h4>
        <p>The Site Layout component provides a generally framework for a NDS page using Twig block statements. The main regions defined in the pattern are header, global_navigation, hero, main, and footer. The block statements that define these regions are only visible in the Twig file. The HTML structure of Site Layout is very plain, allowing you to define your own markup with almost full flexibility:</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" with
            {
                "component_snippet_show_rendered": "no"
            }
        %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/layouts/layouts-site/_layouts-site-main.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Main Layout</h4>
        <p>The Main Layout component defines the major sections of an NDS page. The component provides three main columns: left, main, and right.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" with
            {
                "component_snippet_show_rendered": "no"
            }
        %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/layouts/layouts-main/_layouts-main-main.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Body Card</h4>
        <p>The Body Card component is used to display a page's main content. This component handles padding at various breakpoints, ensuring a visually appealing experience regardless of device or browser.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" with
            {
                "component_snippet_show_rendered": "no"
            }
        %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/layouts/layouts-body/_layouts-body-main.twig" with
                    {
                        "layouts_body_vertical_padding": "yes"
                    }
                %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>
{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-links"
